RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT DISTINCT CUSIP_NO FROM TLTBS_CONTRACT_MASTER A, TLTBS_CONTRACT_FEE_MASTER B WHERE B.FEE_TYPE = 'AM' AND A.CONTRACT_REF_NO = B.CONTRACT_REF_NO AND A.BRANCH = GLOBAL.CURRENT_BRANCH AND CUSIP_NO IS NOT NULL ORDER BY CUSIP_NO
SELECT DISTINCT EXPENSE_CODE FROM TLTBS_CONTRACT_MASTER WHERE EXPENSE_CODE IS NOT NULL AND BRANCH = GLOBAL.CURRENT_BRANCH ORDER BY EXPENSE_CODE
SELECT POSITION_IDENTIFIER FROM TLTMS_POSITION_IDENTIFIER WHERE RECORD_STAT='O' AND AUTH_STAT='A' ORDER BY POSITION_IDENTIFIER
SELECT DESK_CODE FROM LBTMS_DESK WHERE RECORD_STAT='O' AND AUTH_STAT='A' ORDER BY DESK_CODE
SELECT BRANCH_CODE FROM OLTMS_BRANCH WHERE RECORD_STAT='O' AND AUTH_STAT = 'A' ORDER BY BRANCH_CODE
SELECT DISTINCT POSITION_QUALIFIER FROM TLTBS_CONTRACT_MASTER WHERE POSITION_QUALIFIER IS NOT NULL AND BRANCH = GLOBAL.CURRENT_BRANCH ORDER BY POSITION_QUALIFIER
